title: Grateful Dead Live at Hartford Civic Center on 1977-05-28
description:
Set 1

Bertha-> Good Lovin'-> Sugaree, Jack Straw, Row Jimmy, Minglewood Blues, Candyman, Passenger, Brown Eyed Women, Promised Land

Set 2

Samson & Delilah, Tennessee Jed, Estimated Prophet-> Playin' In The Band-> Terrapin Station-> Not Fade Away-> Wharf Rat-> Playin' In The Band-> One More Saturday Night, E: U.S. Blues

reviews.review_text:
There I remember a person with a Hartford Whalers jersey  on next to me 
Whenever the music stopped between songs I kept looking at that jersey thinking of Bob & the wailers 
Funny thing that stuff will do to you 
The Dead were outstanding 
The trump virus must be defeated 
86
